	<h2> Intro: </h2>
	<p> The much anticipated anime movie screening of  <i> Your Name </i> (Kimi no Na Wa) after a very successful One Piece: Gear 5 screening the previous year took place on an unusually enthusiastic Monday night of 12th August, 2024. A housefull Netaji Auditorium witnessed one of the most beloved and visually stunning anime films of all time on a big screen, as the event drew a diverse crowd of students eager to immerse themselves in the film’s emotional and mystical journey.</p>
    <div class="image-container">
		<img src="/assets/events/your-name/1.jpg" alt="">
