	<h2> Conclusion: </h2>
	<p> The screening of <i>Your Name</i> marked yet another milestone for anime culture at IIT Kharagpur. By providing an immersive and memorable experience, MASK once again demonstrated their commitment to fostering a strong anime culture on campus. With this event's success, there’s no doubt that future anime screenings will continue to bring students together, creating lasting memories and deepening their appreciation for the art form. </p>
